summary: I'm sorry but you know who was the real shield that guarded the realms of men? Daenerys Targaryen. Grey Worm and all the...
body: I’m sorry but you know who was the real shield that guarded the realms of men? Daenerys Targaryen. Grey Worm and all the Unsullied. The Dothraki. Drogon. Rhaegal. summary: I was at the mall, in Hot Topic, looking through the GOT shirts.  I had a Targaryen sigil tee in my hand and this young girl...
body:
I was at the mall, in Hot Topic, looking through the GOT shirts.  I had a Targaryen sigil tee in my hand and this young girl comes up and starts looking at them too.  Then, she says the saddest thing.

“I can’t wear this at school, I’ll get judged.”

I wanted to cry.  Listen to me, young queen, you wear whatever you want.  If people judge you, light em up with your pride.  Dracarys!

Seriously though.  People run around with Imperial stickers on their cars, Darth Vader tshirts, etc.  This should be no different.  People need to learn to chill and allow fans to just be fans and show their love. I’m a little tired of fandom being a morality horse race.  Lord.

summary: Just curious if when Dany is resurrected, what do y’all want to happen? I’ve seen some people want her to go back to Westeros...
body:
Just curious if when Dany is resurrected, what do y’all want to happen? I’ve seen some people want her to go back to Westeros and get revenge, some wants her to return to Meereen, some get back together with Jon, or I’ve seen her get back with Daario. I personally would like to see her bring back Valyria and some more dragons. I’d also love to see Missandei come back… but I don’t know how…

Any other thoughts?
